    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.abs(v2) - wp.sin(tmp))
    v2 = (wp.exp(v0) / 0.63)
    v2 = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.10 / v0 + 0.44)) / wp.sin(v0))
    tmp = (0.72 / (0.63 + v2))
    v2 = (0.34 - 0.92)
    data[tid] = v0
